**Summary:**
This documentation explains Amplitude's Lifecycle Chart feature for tracking product user base growth by categorizing active users into new, current, and returning segments, with configuration options for critical events, user segments, and usage intervals, plus three chart views (Growth, Dormant, Pulse).

